---
---
<section id='gallery' class='py-16 bg-white'>
  <div class='max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8'>
    <div class='text-center mb-12'>
      <h2 class='text-3xl font-bold text-orange-900 mb-4'>Memories We've Made</h2>
      <p class='text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg'>A peek into the beautiful chaos, full bellies, and happy faces from our collaborative cooking experiences.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class='grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8'>
      <!-- Review 1 -->
      <div class='bg-orange-50 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-orange-100 flex flex-col justify-between'>
        <div>
          <div class='flex items-center gap-1 text-orange-400 mb-3'>
            &#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;
          </div>
          <p class='text-gray-700 italic mb-4'>"An amazing evening! We hosted 6 friends and cooked Bún Chả together. It was chaotic in the best way possible, filled with stories about Hanoi and lots of laughs."</p>
        </div>
        <p class='font-bold text-gray-900'>- Laura & Friends</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Photo / Placeholder 1 -->
      <div class='rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm h-64 bg-gray-200 relative group'>
        <img src='/images/gallery1.jpg' onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt='Cooking together' class='w-full h-full object-cover transition duration-300 group-hover:scale-105' />
        <div class='absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400 font-medium'>[Photo Placeholder: Happy group]</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Review 2 -->
      <div class='bg-orange-50 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-orange-100 flex flex-col justify-between'>
        <div>
          <div class='flex items-center gap-1 text-orange-400 mb-3'>
            &#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;
          </div>
          <p class='text-gray-700 italic mb-4'>"I never knew making spring rolls could be so fun. The food was 10/10, but the experience of learning the techniques while joking around in our own kitchen made it unforgettable."</p>
        </div>
        <p class='font-bold text-gray-900'>- Marc T.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Photo / Placeholder 2 -->
      <div class='rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm h-64 bg-gray-200 relative group'>
        <img src='/images/gallery2.jpg' onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt='Delicious food' class='w-full h-full object-cover transition duration-300 group-hover:scale-105' />
        <div class='absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400 font-medium'>[Photo Placeholder: Plated Dish]</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Review 3 -->
      <div class='bg-orange-50 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-orange-100 flex flex-col justify-between'>
        <div>
          <div class='flex items-center gap-1 text-orange-400 mb-3'>
            &#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;
          </div>
          <p class='text-gray-700 italic mb-4'>"You host, I teach, we cook - literally the perfect motto. We had the absolute best time wrapping Gỏi Cuốn. The leftovers saved my life the next day!"</p>
        </div>
        <p class='font-bold text-gray-900'>- Sofia M.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Photo / Placeholder 3 -->
      <div class='rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm h-64 bg-gray-200 relative group'>
        <img src='/images/gallery3.jpg' onerror="this.style.display='none'" alt='Cooking action' class='w-full h-full object-cover transition duration-300 group-hover:scale-105' />
        <div class='absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400 font-medium'>[Photo Placeholder: Cooking Action]</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>